<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;m pretty sure it is. Certainly, the book is about John and Washington Roebling, the father and son team that they are playing.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I'm pretty sure it is. Certainly, the book is about John and Washington Roebling, the father and son team that they are playing.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
