<li class='cover' id='bookCover_34237826'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/34237826-grant"><img alt="Grant" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1488289288l/34237826._SX98_.jpg" />
